rComments: This prof is very generous and kind. He makes his lectures interesting and he's helpful. I didn't really like philosophy until he taught it, I wish he could teach all my classes.

The best professor I ever had.  That about wraps it up.  He's enthusiastic, he's clear, he's easy, he'll make anything intersting.  He can be a bit biased towards some topics, but it's all good.  He should be teaching the harder courses, like Biology.  Maybe then more students would be awake.  But seriously, my favourite.

Some of the lectures could get a little boring, it is Philosophy after all, but he did a good job at keeping kids awake. Course load was good, essays were relatively easy, marked them fairly. Knew his material well. Overall, good experience.
